                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-373-18710501 t18710501-373-punishment-15"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">and to find two sureties in</hi> 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., <hi rend="italic">to keep the peace for twelve months</hi>
                  </rs>.</p>
